name: New World
description: Exoconsciousness: Natural ability to tune in, connect and co-create with multidimensional beings. It is not about spiritual retreats, thinking that it is an enlightened being or religions, but the realization of our natural talents in our daily lives, bringing values that go beyond what can be priced in our society, through meditation and attunement with these multidimensional beings and bring practical solutions to our society
